params.to: list of addresses to airdrop to

params.tokenId: id of token to get render address for

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params.isKnown: flag if the above marketplaces are known

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

params.user: address to get Zorb SVG for

airdrop(address[]).notice: Public airdrop of tokens to _other_ addresses

getZorbRenderAddress(uint256).notice: Determines the actual rendering address instead of just owner address for given zorb id

mintIsOpen().notice: Informational function returning if the mint is currently ongoing

tokenURI(uint256).notice: TokenURI function returning on-chain encoded SVG for each Zorb

zorbForAddress(address).notice: Public getter for getting the given Zorb for an address
